premise_source_doc_sentence: Unlike most superheroes , Batman does not possess any superpowers ; rather , he relies on his genius intellect , physical prowess , martial arts abilities , detective skills , science and technology , vast wealth , intimidation , and indomitable will .

He has also been included in several books on the martial arts , such as `` The Original Martial Arts Encyclopedia-Traditions , History , Pioneers ''  (  c  )  1993 by John Corcoran & Emil Farkas and `` The Ultimate Martial Arts Q&A Book ''  (  c  )  2001 by John Corcoran and John Graden .
Federation of Georgian Martial Arts aims renewal and popularization of Georgian martial traditions and methods and upbringing of new generation according to the martial arts traditions .
